  "title": "site supervisor",
  "description": "<p>Assist and support Project Manager in handling and monitoring the progress of project.</p><p>· Has experience with carpentry work.</p><p>· Able to understand RC structural drawing, specification and calculate the costing</p><p>· Able to lead a team of workers</p><p>· Ensure smooth progress of site works.</p><p>· Assessing and managing safety hazards.</p><p>· Completing records for site reports.</p><p>· Attending site management meetings.</p><p>· Control and maintain the safe and smooth progress of works.</p><p>· To co-ordinate with clients, sub-contractors and workers on all project aspects to ensure smooth and timely implementation.</p><p>· Handle project documentation, monitoring of site activities, material requisition, cost control, project supervision and schedule of works.</p><p>· Any other ad-hoc duties that may be assigned from time to time.</p><p><em><strong>Job Requirement:</strong></em></p><p>· Min 10 years of relevant working experience</p><p>· Shift work and weekend duty is required</p><p>. Able to speak in Mandarin, English and simple Bengali as he need to communicate with chinese and bangladeshi workers</p>",
